headline: Top Equity REIT Stocks to Buy as Market Conditions Improve
summary: PLD and two other REITs stand to gain as the demand for industrial, data center and healthcare assets rises, supported by disciplined capital and low rates.

headline: Highwoods Banks on Acquisitions, Boosts Long-Term Growth Trajectory
summary: HIW boosts its portfolio with JV acquisitions in Raleigh and Dallas, targeting accretive cash flow while recycling capital from non-core asset sales.
